    <p class="c6"><span class="c1">What is Software?</span></p>
    <p class="c6">
        <span class="c2">
            Software is a collection of data or computer instructions that tell the computer how to work. This is in contrast to
            physical hardware, from which the system is built and actually performs the work. Software includes all types of
            programs used by computers and related devices.
        </span>
    </p>

